1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,490 --> 00:01:40,950
[Strange Tales of Tang Dynasty II To the West]

3
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:44,030
[Episode 24]

4
00:01:44,270 --> 00:01:46,630
People of Hanzhou City, listen up!

5
00:01:47,630 --> 00:01:49,390
I am a descendant of Duan Gui,

6
00:01:50,789 --> 00:01:52,630
the leader of the Taiyin Sect.

7
00:01:53,100 --> 00:01:55,250
Open the city gates at once.

8
00:01:56,090 --> 00:01:57,950
Those who welcome me into the city

9
00:01:57,990 --> 00:01:59,110
shall be spared.

10
00:01:59,630 --> 00:02:01,470
Those who help me capture

11
00:02:01,510 --> 00:02:03,370
officials of all ranks in Hanzhou

12
00:02:03,510 --> 00:02:04,850
will be rewarded with silver.

13
00:02:04,850 --> 00:02:06,550
The one who kills Lu Si'an

14
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,430
will be rewarded with gold.

15
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:09,160
How dare you!

16
00:02:09,310 --> 00:02:10,560
Linghu, you petty thief,

17
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:12,590
how dare you impersonate a descendant of Duan Gui and plot a rebellion!

18
00:02:12,590 --> 00:02:13,650
My surname is Duan.

19
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:15,790
Who is the one talking nonsense on the city wall?

20
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,930
[Hanzhou]

21
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,670
It is the one who traveled with you to Mount Taiyin,

22
00:02:17,670 --> 00:02:18,630
Lu Lingfeng!

23
00:02:19,230 --> 00:02:19,960
Linghu Shuo,

24
00:02:20,230 --> 00:02:22,430
if you have the guts, take off your mask.

25
00:02:22,630 --> 00:02:24,990
You're the spoiled young heir of Jiufang Pavilion.

26
00:02:24,990 --> 00:02:26,190
Who doesn't know you?

27
00:02:28,010 --> 00:02:28,650
This...

28
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:33,020
What is going on here?

29
00:02:33,310 --> 00:02:34,110
This...

30
00:02:34,550 --> 00:02:35,030
Yeah.

31
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:36,770
What's happening?

32
00:02:36,829 --> 00:02:37,960
Don't listen to him!

33
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,300
Those disloyal to the sect leader

34
00:02:40,750 --> 00:02:41,470
shall die!

35
00:02:50,540 --> 00:02:52,030
Can't you tell?

36
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,680
This Linghu Shuo

37
00:02:54,630 --> 00:02:56,660
just wants to use your identity

38
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,310
to seize control of Hanzhou.

39
00:02:58,590 --> 00:03:00,470
If he succeeds tonight,

40
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:02,520
the first thing he'll do

41
00:03:02,910 --> 00:03:05,150
is kill you to silence you.

42
00:03:05,750 --> 00:03:07,420
Listen, people outside the city.

43
00:03:07,420 --> 00:03:08,430
I know you are all

44
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,470
local civilians.

45
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,640
Life is hard

46
00:03:10,790 --> 00:03:12,430
and you were instigated by evil people.

47
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,390
That's why you went to Mount Taiyin.

48
00:03:14,390 --> 00:03:16,190
The Grand Commander Lu Si'an promises

49
00:03:16,190 --> 00:03:17,740
that as long as you lay down your weapons,

50
00:03:17,740 --> 00:03:19,470
you can all return home to farm.

51
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:20,590
The state government

52
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:22,250
will not pursue your actions.

53
00:03:26,070 --> 00:03:27,530
No one is allowed to leave.

54
00:03:27,910 --> 00:03:30,910
Betraying the sect leader means death without mercy.

55
00:03:31,630 --> 00:03:32,120
Look!

56
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:34,090
The Mountain God is angry.

57
00:03:35,030 --> 00:03:36,110
Listen up!

58
00:03:37,390 --> 00:03:39,690
Once the Mountain God breaks through the city gate,

59
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:41,190
we shall work together

60
00:03:41,870 --> 00:03:43,570
to conquer Hanzhou!

61
00:04:24,110 --> 00:04:24,840
Chicken Fed,

62
00:04:25,460 --> 00:04:26,270
can the medicine

63
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,660
really knock out the Tongtian rhino?

64
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,710
Well...

65
00:04:29,470 --> 00:04:30,390
Who knows?

66
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:33,830
This is all what Su Wuming

67
00:04:33,830 --> 00:04:35,110
told me to say.

68
00:04:38,230 --> 00:04:39,470
Look at that commander.

69
00:04:39,470 --> 00:04:40,870
He looks so calm,

70
00:04:41,630 --> 00:04:43,200
but he's already mentally prepared

71
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,220
to be trampled into ground meat

72
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:45,860
by the Tongtian rhino.

73
00:04:46,790 --> 00:04:48,230
But Lu Lingfeng is still on the city wall.

74
00:04:48,230 --> 00:04:48,670
I—

75
00:04:49,830 --> 00:04:51,960
Su Wuming and Yingtao are there too.

76
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:52,510
So,

77
00:04:53,270 --> 00:04:54,909
you and I cannot go.

78
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:57,120
In life,

79
00:04:57,630 --> 00:04:59,030
we travel west together.

80
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:00,260
In death,

81
00:05:00,910 --> 00:05:02,770
we go to the underworld together.

82
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:19,280
Lu Lingfeng.

83
00:05:20,350 --> 00:05:21,410
What are you doing?

84
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:25,350
According to the mythical beast chart,

85
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:26,410
the Tongtian rhino

86
00:05:26,790 --> 00:05:28,030
has extremely sharp eyesight,

87
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:29,230
loves the moonlight,

88
00:05:29,550 --> 00:05:30,590
and after nightfall,

89
00:05:30,590 --> 00:05:32,970
it fears when the moon is obscured by clouds.

90
00:05:32,970 --> 00:05:33,740
Look,

91
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:34,920
when this cloud

92
00:05:35,790 --> 00:05:37,050
covers the moonlight,

93
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:38,850
it will instantly turn blind.

94
00:05:39,110 --> 00:05:40,840
Then I can kill it with my spear.

95
00:05:41,820 --> 00:05:42,550
Lu Lingfeng,

96
00:05:42,790 --> 00:05:43,790
it was originally

97
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:46,470
just an ordinary saw-toothed rhino.

98
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,550
By absorbing the essence of the sun and moon,

99
00:05:48,550 --> 00:05:50,150
it turned into this form.

100
00:05:50,710 --> 00:05:52,030
That is no easy feat.

101
00:05:52,430 --> 00:05:55,190
Moreover, this rhino has human-like intelligence.

102
00:05:55,190 --> 00:05:56,320
Eighteen years ago,

103
00:05:56,590 --> 00:05:57,870
it once saved the life of

104
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:59,870
a seven-year-old girl.

105
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:01,400
Wouldn't killing it

106
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:04,820
be a pity?

107
00:06:12,910 --> 00:06:14,900
Lu Lingfeng's martial arts are superb,

108
00:06:14,900 --> 00:06:17,050
but it's not guaranteed that he can

109
00:06:17,070 --> 00:06:18,590
kill the Tongtian rhino with his spear.

110
00:06:18,590 --> 00:06:19,510
But look.

111
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:22,950
In an instant, all these Hanzhou soldiers

112
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:24,670
in the city

113
00:06:24,840 --> 00:06:25,910
will either join forces

114
00:06:25,910 --> 00:06:27,110
to kill the Tongtian rhino,

115
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:30,110
or the Tongtian rhino will slaughter the entire city.

116
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:31,280
It will then become

117
00:06:31,350 --> 00:06:34,140
a truly vicious beast of this world.

118
00:06:34,270 --> 00:06:36,230
The Taiyin Sect will also

119
00:06:37,230 --> 00:06:39,030
be cursed by later generations.

120
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:02,870
This time,

121
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:07,000
it will be even more tragic than 18 years ago.

122
00:07:07,810 --> 00:07:09,660
Those incited civilians

123
00:07:09,990 --> 00:07:12,790
will all be executed for treason.

124
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:14,440
And all of this

125
00:07:15,030 --> 00:07:17,510
would just be due to Linghu Shuo's

126
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:19,590
ridiculous ambition.

127
00:07:20,590 --> 00:07:22,030
In my Taiyin Sect,

128
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:24,000
those with merit will be promoted.

129
00:07:24,020 --> 00:07:26,270
Those who kill enemies and make achievements with me

130
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:28,670
will all be founding fathers of my state.

131
00:07:28,910 --> 00:07:31,270
You will be conferred nobility and appointed as ministers.

132
00:07:31,270 --> 00:07:38,390
Kill!

133
00:07:41,180 --> 00:07:42,460
Can't you see

134
00:07:42,630 --> 00:07:44,350
his wild ambition?

135
00:07:52,630 --> 00:07:54,030
Copying the rhino's roar

136
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,710
can only lure the Mountain God out.

137
00:07:55,710 --> 00:07:56,950
But in order to ride the Mountain God

138
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,280
and leave Mount Taiyin,

139
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:02,010
please teach me your unique skill, sect leader.

140
00:08:05,550 --> 00:08:06,110
Ami,

141
00:08:06,500 --> 00:08:08,070
what are you still hesitating for?

142
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,790
If we take down Hanzhou tonight,

143
00:08:09,790 --> 00:08:11,000
you will be the founding emperor

144
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,260
of the State of Taiyin.

145
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:13,470
But I

146
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,470
am a woman.

147
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:18,270
Wu Zetian changed the Tang Dynasty to Zhou.

148
00:08:18,630 --> 00:08:20,260
Why can't you be the first female emperor

149
00:08:20,260 --> 00:08:21,310
of Hanzhou?

150
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:24,390
Our children will inherit the great dynasty

151
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:27,250
and the empire will be passed down the generations.

152
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,400
Time is running out.

153
00:08:54,780 --> 00:08:56,370
You can't stop me.

154
00:08:57,310 --> 00:08:59,070
I am the king of Hanzhou.

155
00:09:00,030 --> 00:09:01,750
I will be the emperor!

156
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,630
You absolutely shouldn't have

157
00:09:09,630 --> 00:09:11,790
taught the skill of controlling the Tongtian rhino

158
00:09:11,790 --> 00:09:13,110
to this madman.

159
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,630
He never loved me.

160
00:09:22,910 --> 00:09:24,510
He just wanted to use me.

161
00:10:34,590 --> 00:10:36,450
What I said earlier still stands.

162
00:10:36,750 --> 00:10:38,150
Those who set down their weapons

163
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,410
and return home to farm

164
00:10:39,830 --> 00:10:41,490
will not be held accountable.

165
00:10:41,910 --> 00:10:42,470
This...

166
00:10:42,710 --> 00:10:43,470
Won't be held accountable?

167
00:10:43,470 --> 00:10:45,230
Attack Hanzhou City with me!

168
00:10:45,850 --> 00:10:48,110
Those who are disloyal to the sect leader

169
00:10:48,110 --> 00:10:48,950
will die!

170
00:10:52,390 --> 00:10:53,050
Go quickly.

171
00:10:53,430 --> 00:10:54,830
Go.

172
00:11:59,590 --> 00:12:00,270
Sheriff Lu,

173
00:12:00,630 --> 00:12:01,490
take the sword.

174
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:23,840
♫The dark hair is messy, the futou is dark♫

175
00:13:24,980 --> 00:13:29,800
♫The horse neighs, the clouds scatter♫

176
00:13:31,040 --> 00:13:36,150
♫Fame and merit are troublesome♫

177
00:13:37,100 --> 00:13:42,790
♫Crossing thousands of mountains♫

178
00:13:43,490 --> 00:13:44,150
Sheriff Lu,

179
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:45,170
you're here.

180
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,070
I came

181
00:13:47,610 --> 00:13:48,740
to return the sword.

182
00:13:52,410 --> 00:13:53,190
This is the sword I forged

183
00:13:53,190 --> 00:13:54,850
that I'm most satisfied with.

184
00:13:55,820 --> 00:13:57,430
The day I became a blacksmith,

185
00:13:57,430 --> 00:13:58,110
I vowed

186
00:13:58,600 --> 00:13:59,590
to forge the best

187
00:13:59,590 --> 00:14:00,650
Heng sword in Tang.

188
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:02,800
But I suppose

189
00:14:02,830 --> 00:14:03,960
you won't think much

190
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,960
of a Heng sword forged by a commoner.

191
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:08,160
Mu, that's nonsense.

192
00:14:09,350 --> 00:14:10,830
This is an excellent sword.

193
00:14:10,830 --> 00:14:11,690
In that case...

194
00:14:11,990 --> 00:14:12,720
Apprentice,

195
00:14:12,800 --> 00:14:13,670
bring the scabbard.

196
00:14:13,670 --> 00:14:14,400
Yes, Master.

197
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,150
Do I have the honor

198
00:14:22,150 --> 00:14:23,630
of gifting this to you?

199
00:14:24,030 --> 00:14:24,490
This...

200
00:14:25,770 --> 00:14:26,950
This isn't appropriate.

201
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:28,010
I forge Heng swords

202
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,490
to slay the wicked,

203
00:14:29,990 --> 00:14:31,450
but I'm just a blacksmith.

204
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:33,030
I can only dream about it.

205
00:14:34,570 --> 00:14:35,170
But now,

206
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:37,150
with this sword in your hands,

207
00:14:37,150 --> 00:14:38,700
it has truly slain the wicked.

208
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:40,630
The people of Hanzhou are all talking about it.

209
00:14:40,630 --> 00:14:42,140
It makes me proud too.

210
00:14:42,950 --> 00:14:43,950
If you don't mind,

211
00:14:44,590 --> 00:14:45,710
let it accompany you

212
00:14:45,710 --> 00:14:46,710
as you charge into battle

213
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:51,560
♫Yellow sand sweep around golden armor♫

214
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:48,930
and make great achievements.

215
00:14:51,770 --> 00:14:57,370
♫The city is aflame, the Heng sword ends the fire♫

216
00:14:57,910 --> 00:15:01,110
♫My heart is like water, ambition like rock♫

217
00:15:01,130 --> 00:15:04,730
♫When I look back, the horizon is far♫

218
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,550
Thank you, Mu.

219
00:15:05,130 --> 00:15:10,730
♫Drunk in the sunset, my heart is full of the beautiful nation♫

220
00:15:09,710 --> 00:15:11,510
Thank you, Sheriff Lu.

221
00:15:14,990 --> 00:15:17,270
Many thanks to the people of Hanzhou.

222
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:29,670
♫Whom to sit with? The moon, wind, you, and I♫

223
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:29,950
Xijun,

224
00:15:30,390 --> 00:15:32,070
the sword Lu Lingfeng used

225
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:33,090
in Nanzhou before

226
00:15:33,190 --> 00:15:34,500
was given by you.

227
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:37,070
I never saw you cherish it so much.

228
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,900
This is different.

229
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,810
This sword carries

230
00:15:40,950 --> 00:15:42,270
the affection and expectations

231
00:15:42,270 --> 00:15:44,070
of the people of Hanzhou for him.

232
00:15:44,150 --> 00:15:46,430
It's more worthy of cherishing than the sword I gifted.

233
00:15:46,430 --> 00:15:47,100
Xijun,

234
00:15:47,940 --> 00:15:50,620
you really make me feel a deep sense of respect.

235
00:15:52,310 --> 00:15:54,150
[Hanzhou County]

236
00:16:01,190 --> 00:16:01,720
Yingtao,

237
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:03,670
I haven't even said I'm leaving yet.

238
00:16:03,670 --> 00:16:04,730
What are you doing?

239
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:06,690
You didn't say you were leaving,

240
00:16:06,690 --> 00:16:07,760
but I think I

241
00:16:08,270 --> 00:16:08,800
should go

242
00:16:08,950 --> 00:16:10,280
What do you mean by this?

243
00:16:11,790 --> 00:16:13,030
You kept holding Ami's hand

244
00:16:13,030 --> 00:16:14,110
and wouldn't let go for even a moment,

245
00:16:14,110 --> 00:16:15,630
and you're asking me what I mean?

246
00:16:15,630 --> 00:16:16,890
There's no such thing.

247
00:16:16,980 --> 00:16:18,380
You're still denying it.

248
00:16:21,150 --> 00:16:22,140
I, Su Wuming,

249
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:23,870
am upright and aboveboard.

250
00:16:23,870 --> 00:16:24,630
I never deny

251
00:16:24,650 --> 00:16:25,510
what I've done.

252
00:16:25,870 --> 00:16:27,840
But I really didn't hold

253
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:28,830
Ami's hand.

254
00:16:29,190 --> 00:16:29,790
I was

255
00:16:29,990 --> 00:16:31,430
gripping her wrist.

256
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:32,550
Plus,

257
00:16:32,970 --> 00:16:34,570
I didn't touch her directly.

258
00:16:38,190 --> 00:16:40,310
Gripping a suspect's wrist

259
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:42,990
as a constable

260
00:16:43,010 --> 00:16:44,190
and holding a woman's hand

261
00:16:44,190 --> 00:16:46,110
are completely different things.

262
00:16:46,110 --> 00:16:46,640
Yingtao,

263
00:16:47,350 --> 00:16:48,630
you're wronging me.

264
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:50,040
It's a huge mistake.

265
00:16:51,580 --> 00:16:52,470
Su Wuming,

266
00:16:52,740 --> 00:16:53,110
I...

267
00:16:54,630 --> 00:16:55,230
Of course,

268
00:16:56,030 --> 00:16:58,000
you also played a part

269
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:59,390
in eliminating the Taiyin Sect.

270
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:00,270
I won't hold you

271
00:17:00,860 --> 00:17:02,590
accountable for this mistake.

272
00:17:03,390 --> 00:17:03,990
By the way,

273
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:06,869
Commander Lu is hosting a banquet tonight.

274
00:17:07,069 --> 00:17:09,109
It's both a welcome and a farewell.

275
00:17:09,670 --> 00:17:10,490
During the banquet,

276
00:17:10,490 --> 00:17:12,440
you should punish yourself with a few more drinks.

277
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,619
I, Su Wuming, am magnanimous

278
00:17:13,619 --> 00:17:15,280
and will let this matter pass.

279
00:17:16,310 --> 00:17:16,990
How...

280
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:20,579
How did it become my wrongdoing?

281
00:18:14,150 --> 00:18:14,950
It is said that

282
00:18:15,190 --> 00:18:16,520
those two giant condors

283
00:18:16,740 --> 00:18:18,600
circled in the sky for a long time.

284
00:18:19,260 --> 00:18:19,860
Suddenly,

285
00:18:20,140 --> 00:18:21,270
one of them dove down

286
00:18:21,500 --> 00:18:24,160
