00:30:04,130 --> 00:30:05,460
How come he's a boss now?

576
00:30:07,470 --> 00:30:08,190
Yes.

577
00:30:08,870 --> 00:30:10,830
Our sheriff Sima Liang

578
00:30:10,910 --> 00:30:13,440
is also the biggest wine merchant in Yunding.

579
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:18,030
It's just that, for some reason,

580
00:30:18,360 --> 00:30:19,470
the imperial court actually

581
00:30:19,470 --> 00:30:20,790
replaced him.

582
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:26,670
[Yunding County Government]

583
00:30:25,910 --> 00:30:26,950
Sheriff Sima.

584
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:30,090
[Yunding County Magistrate, Huangfu Tan]

585
00:30:27,070 --> 00:30:28,710
You must not have

586
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:30,710
any resentment toward me.

587
00:30:32,070 --> 00:30:32,710
How dare I?

588
00:30:32,110 --> 00:30:36,270
[Former Yunding Sheriff, Sima Liang]

589
00:30:33,510 --> 00:30:34,590
Since the court's newly appointed sheriff

590
00:30:34,590 --> 00:30:35,790
will arrive soon,

591
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:38,430
I, who should've resigned long ago,

592
00:30:38,430 --> 00:30:39,430
can finally go

593
00:30:39,430 --> 00:30:40,360
and be carefree.

594
00:30:40,670 --> 00:30:42,070
Why would I be resentful?

595
00:30:42,190 --> 00:30:42,870
Besides,

596
00:30:43,000 --> 00:30:44,480
there was an accident in the case file room.

597
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:46,190
I'm already endlessly grateful

598
00:30:46,190 --> 00:30:47,650
that you didn't punish me.

599
00:30:48,980 --> 00:30:50,270
I never said

600
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:51,740
I wouldn't punish you.

601
00:30:51,910 --> 00:30:54,110
It's just that I won't pursue the matter

602
00:30:54,230 --> 00:30:56,090
because of you years of hard work.

603
00:30:56,510 --> 00:30:57,840
Thank you, Magistrate.

604
00:30:58,190 --> 00:30:58,990
Sima,

605
00:30:59,070 --> 00:31:00,710
what are your plans for the future?

606
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:02,040
What other plans can I have?

607
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:03,510
I only hope to sell the fine wine of Yunding

608
00:31:03,510 --> 00:31:04,390
to Chang'an,

609
00:31:05,230 --> 00:31:05,760
Luoyang,

610
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:08,650
and even throughout the entire Tang.

611
00:31:10,070 --> 00:31:11,200
That's my only wish.

612
00:31:11,390 --> 00:31:13,320
The road ahead is long and arduous.

613
00:31:14,310 --> 00:31:15,240
It's difficult,

614
00:31:15,750 --> 00:31:17,070
but once it's done,

615
00:31:17,350 --> 00:31:20,680
Yunding will surely become renowned throughout the world.

616
00:31:21,140 --> 00:31:22,070
I'll hold a banquet tonight

617
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:23,940
[Yunding Assistant of County Magistrate, Song Shang]

618
00:31:22,230 --> 00:31:23,890
and Mr. Song will accompany me

619
00:31:24,430 --> 00:31:26,710
to toast to your grand ambition

620
00:31:26,790 --> 00:31:28,650
and drink to our heart's content.

621
00:31:28,750 --> 00:31:30,010
I'm honored to oblige.

622
00:31:54,270 --> 00:31:55,060
Ladies and gentlemen,

623
00:31:55,060 --> 00:31:56,520
what would you like to eat?

624
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:58,080
One serving of each of

625
00:31:58,110 --> 00:31:59,510
Yunding's signature dishes.

626
00:31:59,510 --> 00:32:00,660
More importantly,

627
00:32:01,100 --> 00:32:02,910
bring me the Yunding Red.

628
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:04,410
That's what I came for.

629
00:32:04,990 --> 00:32:05,650
Sure thing.

630
00:32:12,410 --> 00:32:15,280
[Dancer, Qing Xi]

631
00:32:25,600 --> 00:32:27,590
Look at these wine vessels.

632
00:32:27,590 --> 00:32:28,790
They are all so exquisite.

633
00:32:28,790 --> 00:32:29,420
The wine

634
00:32:29,790 --> 00:32:31,550
must go without saying,

635
00:32:31,610 --> 00:32:32,120
right?

636
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:32,840
Come.

637
00:32:32,870 --> 00:32:33,430
Come.

638
00:32:33,470 --> 00:32:34,910
Let me pour the wine for you.

639
00:32:34,910 --> 00:32:35,440
Fed,

640
00:32:35,990 --> 00:32:37,470
you are the elder.

641
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:39,520
It's not your responsibility.

642
00:32:42,290 --> 00:32:43,030
Let me do it.

643
00:32:43,710 --> 00:32:44,270
Yingtao.

644
00:32:45,120 --> 00:32:45,850
Give it to me.

645
00:32:48,370 --> 00:32:49,580
You do it?

646
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:51,420
What's the reasoning?

647
00:32:51,420 --> 00:32:52,750
Waiter, bring the wine!

648
00:32:53,870 --> 00:32:54,510
Coming!

649
00:32:56,420 --> 00:32:57,880
On this journey to the west

650
00:32:58,750 --> 00:33:00,480
you all followed me to Yunding,

651
00:33:00,980 --> 00:33:03,410
facing hardships, dangers, and multiple crises

652
00:33:03,410 --> 00:33:04,270
along the way.

653
00:33:06,110 --> 00:33:07,950
I, Lu Lingfeng, am not good with words,

654
00:33:07,950 --> 00:33:08,920
but my gratitude

655
00:33:09,310 --> 00:33:10,310
is all in my heart.

656
00:33:11,440 --> 00:33:12,900
Let me pour the wine for you

657
00:33:13,030 --> 00:33:14,090
to show my respect.

658
00:33:19,520 --> 00:33:20,500
I have

659
00:33:20,750 --> 00:33:21,990
lived for so long.

660
00:33:22,790 --> 00:33:24,190
If I hadn't met you all,

661
00:33:24,470 --> 00:33:26,530
I would definitely still be alone now

662
00:33:26,860 --> 00:33:29,660
and whiling my days away in the gloomy Ghost Market

663
00:33:29,710 --> 00:33:31,070
of Chang'an.

664
00:33:32,280 --> 00:33:33,040
Fed, you...

665
00:33:33,260 --> 00:33:34,790
Now that you put it that way,

666
00:33:35,390 --> 00:33:36,270
I'm also getting—

667
00:33:36,270 --> 00:33:36,750
Enough.

668
00:33:37,260 --> 00:33:39,260
Stop pretending to be sentimental.

669
00:33:40,330 --> 00:33:41,150
Today, let us

670
00:33:42,100 --> 00:33:43,760
drink to our heart's content.

671
00:33:44,060 --> 00:33:44,860
Yes, yes, yes.

672
00:33:45,030 --> 00:33:45,790
Let's drink.

673
00:33:47,310 --> 00:33:48,720
Let's wish Lu Lingfeng

674
00:33:49,070 --> 00:33:51,990
a smooth start in office tomorrow morning

675
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:54,810
and wish us all a carefree time

676
00:33:55,300 --> 00:33:56,750
in Yunding.

677
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:59,320
A carefree time. Well said.

678
00:33:59,470 --> 00:33:59,830
Come.

679
00:34:00,070 --> 00:34:00,550
Cheers!

680
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,540
It is indeed good wine.

681
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,510
Still the same taste

682
00:34:15,540 --> 00:34:16,710
So ignorant.

683
00:34:17,300 --> 00:34:18,989
He thinks Yunding Red

684
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:20,670
is the limit.

685
00:34:21,310 --> 00:34:23,190
After all, you need money

686
00:34:23,389 --> 00:34:25,120
to drink Eternal Drunkenness.

687
00:34:26,210 --> 00:34:27,050
Come.

688
00:34:29,150 --> 00:34:29,630
Sirs,

689
00:34:30,489 --> 00:34:31,889
what was the drunkenness

690
00:34:32,350 --> 00:34:33,550
you just mentioned?

691
00:34:34,310 --> 00:34:35,870
Eternal Drunkenness.

692
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:37,449
Eternal Drunkenness?

693
00:34:37,750 --> 00:34:39,600
Is it even better than Yunding Red?

694
00:34:39,600 --> 00:34:41,139
No matter how good Yunding Red is,

695
00:34:41,139 --> 00:34:42,909
it's still made from grapes.

696
00:34:43,030 --> 00:34:44,550
Eternal Drunkenness...

697
00:34:45,030 --> 00:34:45,830
Of course, it's also

698
00:34:45,830 --> 00:34:46,830
made from grapes.

699
00:34:47,310 --> 00:34:48,110
It's just that

700
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:50,139
the brewing method is different.

701
00:34:50,139 --> 00:34:50,850
Drinking it

702
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:53,630
can nourish one's soul and prolong life.

703
00:34:54,139 --> 00:34:55,510
Otherwise, why would we

704
00:34:55,520 --> 00:34:56,909
travel for so long to come here?

705
00:34:56,909 --> 00:34:57,630
Exactly.

706
00:34:58,270 --> 00:34:59,930
You're just bluffing, right?

707
00:35:00,350 --> 00:35:01,380
How come

708
00:35:01,790 --> 00:35:03,510
I've never heard of Eternal Drunkenness before?

709
00:35:03,510 --> 00:35:05,150
You're ignorant and ill-informed.

710
00:35:05,150 --> 00:35:07,140
It's a top-quality wine brewed

711
00:35:07,180 --> 00:35:08,390
with ancient techniques

712
00:35:08,390 --> 00:35:10,830
on the basis of Yunding Red.

713
00:35:13,270 --> 00:35:14,180
Come, come.

714
00:35:14,430 --> 00:35:15,830
Let's change to some good wine.

715
00:35:15,830 --> 00:35:16,500
Waiter!

716
00:35:20,020 --> 00:35:21,910
Bring a jar of Eternal Drunkenness.

717
00:35:21,910 --> 00:35:22,550
Well,

718
00:35:22,950 --> 00:35:24,610
we really don't have it today.

719
00:35:25,110 --> 00:35:26,240
You'll have to wait.

720
00:35:26,270 --> 00:35:27,500
But it's expensive.

721
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:28,810
Expensive?

722
00:35:29,150 --> 00:35:30,470
How expensive can it be?

723
00:35:30,470 --> 00:35:32,070
A jar of Eternal Drunkenness

724
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:34,350
costs as much as ten jars of Yunding Red.

725
00:35:36,290 --> 00:35:38,270
Wine this expensive can't possibly taste good.

726
00:35:38,270 --> 00:35:38,710
Alright,

727
00:35:38,710 --> 00:35:39,680
you can go.

728
00:35:39,950 --> 00:35:41,270
Don't be impatient, Fei.

729
00:35:41,270 --> 00:35:42,710
Sooner or later, we'll drink

730
00:35:42,710 --> 00:35:44,040
all the wine in Yunding.

731
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:46,340
Sheriff Lu,

732
00:35:46,780 --> 00:35:49,580
you said earlier to drink to oour hearts' content.

733
00:35:50,070 --> 00:35:50,670
Why don't we

734
00:35:50,670 --> 00:35:52,000
stay here for the night?

735
00:35:52,470 --> 00:35:53,750
Secretary Su, please

736
00:35:53,950 --> 00:35:55,150
book the rooms for us.

737
00:35:55,710 --> 00:35:56,270
Yes, sir.

738
00:36:00,270 --> 00:36:01,000
Shopkeeper,

739
00:36:01,270 --> 00:36:02,800
we need two superior rooms.

740
00:36:03,110 --> 00:36:04,630
We happen to have two left.

741
00:36:05,150 --> 00:36:05,630
Great.

742
00:36:24,870 --> 00:36:25,930
They are upstairs.

743
00:36:29,110 --> 00:36:30,970
Why did you stop dancing, Qing Xi?

744
00:36:31,270 --> 00:36:32,470
I have to go back now.

745
00:36:34,090 --> 00:36:35,690
I forgot about your husband.

746
00:36:36,310 --> 00:36:36,950
So,

747
00:36:37,470 --> 00:36:39,070
my wages for these ten days...

748
00:36:39,070 --> 00:36:40,470
Others get paid monthly.

749
00:36:40,550 --> 00:36:42,810
But you, Qing Xi, get paid every ten days.

750
00:36:43,270 --> 00:36:45,310
You're lucky to have met me.

751
00:36:45,550 --> 00:36:46,310
Shopkeeper,

752
00:36:47,310 --> 00:36:48,950
Qing Xi is beautiful

753
00:36:49,510 --> 00:36:50,950
and she dances well.

754
00:36:52,150 --> 00:36:54,550
What's wrong with paying her every ten days?

755
00:36:54,550 --> 00:36:56,510
If she could dance in my home,

756
00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:58,400
I'd pay her daily.

757
00:36:58,900 --> 00:36:59,910
You're right.

758
00:37:00,320 --> 00:37:02,190
I got the good end of the bargain

759
00:37:02,230 --> 00:37:03,890
with Qing Xi dancing at my inn.

760
00:37:05,070 --> 00:37:05,590
Here,

761
00:37:06,350 --> 00:37:06,870
Qing Xi.

762
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:07,830
Take this.

763
00:37:21,620 --> 00:37:22,310
Robbery!

764
00:37:22,340 --> 00:37:22,900
Qing Xi!

765
00:37:24,190 --> 00:37:25,050
What happened?

766
00:37:25,070 --> 00:37:27,130
The man in front robbed me of my money.

767
00:37:37,870 --> 00:37:39,590
Mind your own business.

768
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:43,000
If you don't want to die

769
00:37:43,030 --> 00:37:44,510
under my steel fork,

770
00:37:45,030 --> 00:37:47,030
obediently hand over the money.

771
00:37:45,100 --> 00:37:46,950
[Huntsman, Jin Bao]

772
00:37:47,490 --> 00:37:49,960
[Ruffian, Huang You]

773
00:37:48,270 --> 00:37:48,870
I'll pay.

774
00:37:50,050 --> 00:37:51,050
I'll hand it over.

775
00:37:58,390 --> 00:37:58,990
Jin Bao.

776
00:38:00,350 --> 00:38:01,010
Here you go.

777
00:38:03,390 --> 00:38:05,470
In the future, tuck your money pouch inside your clothes.

778
00:38:05,470 --> 00:38:06,110
Thank you.

779
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:07,670
Don't mention it.

780
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:09,630
Where are you going?

781
00:38:09,650 --> 00:38:11,250
I just got back from dancing.

782
00:38:11,350 --> 00:38:12,470
Today is payday.

783
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:14,750
By the way,

784
00:38:15,350 --> 00:38:16,840
how is Bao Kang's leg?

785
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:18,750
It's been over two months.

786
00:38:18,750 --> 00:38:20,080
I was going to visit him,

787
00:38:20,630 --> 00:38:21,390
but...

788
00:38:22,350 --> 00:38:23,470
From now on,

789
00:38:24,520 --> 00:38:26,250
he will probably be bedridden.

790
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:28,240
He really can't stand up anymore?

791
00:38:31,670 --> 00:38:32,150
Here.

792
00:38:33,030 --> 00:38:33,590
No need.

793
00:38:34,260 --> 00:38:35,860
Use it make soup for Bao Kang.

794
00:38:35,990 --> 00:38:36,450
Take it.

795
00:38:36,590 --> 00:38:37,510
I really don't need it.

796
00:38:37,510 --> 00:38:38,150
I know

797
00:38:38,390 --> 00:38:39,460
Bao Kang is usually frugal.

798
00:38:39,460 --> 00:38:40,860
He doesn't buy anything,

799
00:38:41,470 --> 00:38:42,670
but he's injured now.

800
00:38:42,680 --> 00:38:44,610
How can he not eat some good things?

801
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,510
Thank you, Jin Bao.

802
00:39:03,940 --> 00:39:05,150
Huang You, get up.

803
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:07,210
Don't play dead with me.

804
00:39:24,010 --> 00:39:27,230
[Qing Xi’s husband, Bao Kang]

805
00:39:40,630 --> 00:39:41,430
Thank you.

806
00:39:42,590 --> 00:39:44,190
I'm not afraid of suffering,

807
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:46,440
but you can't be so stubborn anymore.

808
00:39:51,470 --> 00:39:52,800
How am I being stubborn?

809
00:39:54,710 --> 00:39:56,110
Think about it yourself.

810
00:40:01,670 --> 00:40:03,070
This chicken is so fresh.

811
00:40:03,550 --> 00:40:05,210
It must be a mountain chicken.

812
00:40:07,150 --> 00:40:08,750
Don't tell me you bought it.

813
00:40:09,110 --> 00:40:10,240
Jin Bao gave it to me.

814
00:40:10,510 --> 00:40:12,040
He told me to stew it for you.

815
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:17,040
He came to our house?

816
00:40:17,710 --> 00:40:18,230
No.

817
00:40:19,110 --> 00:40:20,490
I got robbed on the way back

818
00:40:20,490 --> 00:40:21,910
from the inn.

819
00:40:22,270 --> 00:40:24,190
Jin Bao happened to return from hunting.

820
00:40:24,190 --> 00:40:26,190
He helped me get my money pouch back.

821
00:40:27,070 --> 00:40:28,390
What a coincidence.

822
00:40:31,710 --> 00:40:33,640
You shouldn't go dancing anymore.

823
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,390
You're disabled from the fall.

824
00:40:36,390 --> 00:40:37,590
If I don't go out to dance,

825
00:40:37,590 --> 00:40:38,750
we'll use up all our savings.

826
00:40:38,750 --> 00:40:39,910
I'm disabled,

827
00:40:40,820 --> 00:40:42,550
but I'm not useless.

828
00:40:46,110 --> 00:40:47,150
I misspoke.

829
00:40:47,430 --> 00:40:49,690
I'm afraid that's what you really think.

830
00:40:57,430 --> 00:40:59,830
If you ask me, we should go see a doctor first

831
00:41:00,030 --> 00:41:01,230
and have your legs checked.

832
00:41:01,230 --> 00:41:01,750
I won't.

833
00:41:02,350 --> 00:41:03,670
It's already like this.

834
00:41:03,670 --> 00:41:05,070
What's the point of getting it checked?

835
00:41:05,070 --> 00:41:06,690
It's precisely because you broke your leg before

836
00:41:06,690 --> 00:41:07,390
and didn't get it looked at

837
00:41:07,390 --> 00:41:08,530
that it turned out this way.

838
00:41:08,530 --> 00:41:10,020
These legs can't recover

839
00:41:10,270 --> 00:41:11,470
and I can't stand up anymore.

840
00:41:11,470 --> 00:41:13,550
Even if I see a doctor, I still won't be able to stand.

841
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:14,880
You better be prepared.

842
00:41:21,990 --> 00:41:23,350
Are you done reading this book?

843
00:41:23,350 --> 00:41:24,350
I'll go return it.

844
00:41:24,630 --> 00:41:26,830
One more night means one more day's fee.

845
00:41:27,070 --> 00:41:28,880
Stop saying these useless things.

846
00:41:28,880 --> 00:41:30,630
You look down on me

847
00:41:30,650 --> 00:41:31,510
because I'm disabled.

848
00:41:31,510 --> 00:41:33,190
Isn't that why you don't want to stay at home?

849
00:41:33,190 --> 00:41:35,040
If you have the guts, go to Jin Bao.

850
00:41:35,040 --> 00:41:35,970
His legs are fine

851
00:41:35,990 --> 00:41:36,910
and he's strong.

852
00:41:36,910 --> 00:41:38,310
Don't think I don't know.

853
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,350
You shameless woman,

854
00:41:39,350 --> 00:41:40,590
you've been messing around with him for a long time.

855
00:41:40,590 --> 00:41:41,550
The one you think about every day

856
00:41:41,550 --> 00:41:42,680
is Jin Bao, isn't it?

857
00:41:42,750 --> 00:41:43,230
You...

858
00:41:44,910 --> 00:41:45,640
Ridiculous.

859
00:42:15,080 --> 00:42:15,640
Who is it?

860
00:42:22,270 --> 00:42:23,390
Qing Xi, it's me,

861
00:42:24,030 --> 00:42:25,360
Wang Qiu from next door.

862
00:42:25,950 --> 00:42:27,190
What are you doing,

863
00:42:27,510 --> 00:42:28,590
sneaking into my house?

864
00:42:28,480 --> 00:42:31,490
[Wang Qiu, neighbor of Qing Xi]

865
00:42:28,610 --> 00:42:29,050
I...

866
00:42:30,180 --> 00:42:32,310
I wanted to borrow your kitchen knife.

867
00:42:33,870 --> 00:42:34,930
To slaughter a pig.

868
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:36,470
The one I have at home

869
00:42:36,680 --> 00:42:37,490
is too blunt.

870
00:42:39,110 --> 00:42:40,590
Next time, knock before entering the courtyard.

871
00:42:40,590 --> 00:42:41,390
I did knock.

872
00:42:42,670 --> 00:42:44,230
You didn't hear it.

873
00:42:47,830 --> 00:42:49,120
How is Bao Kang's leg?

874
00:42:50,510 --> 00:42:52,310
You're calling him Bao Kang now?

875
00:42:52,370 --> 00:42:53,110
Don't you realize

876
00:42:53,110 --> 00:42:54,470
how much younger you are than him?

877
00:42:54,470 --> 00:42:55,430
Alright.

878
00:42:56,740 --> 00:42:59,230
Then how is Brother-in-law Bao Kang's leg doing?

879
00:42:59,230 --> 00:43:00,340
Don't worry too much.

880
00:43:00,340 --> 00:43:01,360
After I slaughter the pig,

881
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:03,350
I'll bring over a big pig trotter for you.

882
00:43:03,350 --> 00:43:04,830
And who said I was your sister?

883
00:43:04,830 --> 00:43:06,760
Why are you bringing a pig trotter?

884
00:43:06,790 --> 00:43:08,820
To help nourish Brother-in-law Bao Kang, of course.

885
00:43:08,820 --> 00:43:09,880
As the saying goes,

886
00:43:10,830 --> 00:43:11,550
eat what

887
00:43:12,020 --> 00:43:12,550
you lack.

888
00:43:13,590 --> 00:43:15,120
Well, I must thank you then.

889
00:43:15,230 --> 00:43:16,830
Keep it to nourish yourself.

890
00:43:21,510 --> 00:43:23,570
Return it after you're done using it.

891
00:43:25,150 --> 00:43:26,150
Qing Xi,

892
00:43:26,870 --> 00:43:27,880
I wasn't joking.

893
00:43:28,110 --> 00:43:28,950
After butchering the pig,

894
00:43:28,950 --> 00:43:30,790
I really will bring over a pig trotter.

895
00:43:30,790 --> 00:43:31,630
Just one?

896
00:43:32,070 --> 00:43:33,790
You want Brother-in-law Bao Kang to eat it

897
00:43:33,790 --> 00:43:34,720
and then I eat it?

898
00:43:34,870 --> 00:43:35,730
Or should I eat it

899
00:43:35,730 --> 00:43:37,070
and then Brother-in-law Bao Kang eats it?

900
00:43:37,070 --> 00:43:38,790
Then I'll bring two.

901
00:43:41,190 --> 00:43:42,030
Actually,

902
00:43:42,330 --> 00:43:43,280
I wish I could turn myself

903
00:43:43,280 --> 00:43:44,070
into a pig trotter

904
00:43:44,070 --> 00:43:45,150
for you to eat.

905
00:43:45,700 --> 00:43:47,680
You little brat, trying to take advantage of me.

906
00:43:47,680 --> 00:43:48,370
I'm not lending you the knife anymore.

907
00:43:48,370 --> 00:43:48,970
No, no, no!

908
00:43:49,310 --> 00:43:50,630
Look at me. I let my guard down

909
00:43:50,630 --> 00:43:52,180
and spoke what was really on my mind.

910
00:43:52,180 --> 00:43:52,620
You—
